</p>
<h3>iOS</h3>
<ol>
<li>Open Safari</li>
<li>Navigate to your Home Assistant instance</li>
<li>Tap on the Share icon in the middle of the bottom toolbar</li>
<li>Tap on â€œAdd to Home Screenâ€</li>
<li>A dialog will popup; tap on Add</li>
</ol>
